{"image_id": "BXP_2007_page_51", "image_size": [1275, 1650], "ocr": [{"text": "We face possible state and local tax audits.", "bbox": [162.5, 158.9, 528.8, 179.7]}, {"text": "Because we are organized and qualify as a REIT, we are generally not subject to federal income taxes, but", "bbox": [204.2, 197.6, 1090.7, 218.4]}, {"text": "are subject to certain state and local taxes. In the normal course of business, certain entities through which we", "bbox": [162.5, 222.6, 1078.6, 243.4]}, {"text": "own real estate either have undergone, or are currently undergoing, tax audits. Although we believe that we have", "bbox": [162.5, 247.6, 1103.5, 268.4]}, {"text": "substantial arguments in favor of our positions in the ongoing audits, in some instances there is no controlling", "bbox": [162.5, 272.6, 1078.4, 293.4]}, {"text": "precedent or interpretive guidance on the specific point at issue. Collectively, tax deficiency notices received to", "bbox": [162.5, 297.6, 1093.1, 318.4]}, {"text": "date from the jurisdictions conducting the ongoing audits have not been material. However, there can be no", "bbox": [162.5, 322.6, 1058.5, 343.4]}, {"text": "assurance that future audits will not occur with increased frequency or that the ultimate result of such audits will", "bbox": [162.5, 347.6, 1100.7, 368.4]}, {"text": "not have a material adverse effect on our results of operations.", "bbox": [162.5, 372.6, 682.4, 393.4]}, {"text": "Item 1B.", "bbox": [162.5, 438.2, 239.0, 459.1]}, {"text": "Unresolved Staff Comments.", "bbox": [256.2, 438.2, 502.4, 459.1]}, {"text": "None.", "bbox": [204.2, 477.0, 254.5, 497.8]}, {"text": "Item 2.", "bbox": [162.5, 542.6, 225.1, 563.4]}, {"text": "Properties", "bbox": [256.2, 542.6, 344.2, 563.4]}, {"text": "At December 31, 2007, our portfolio consisted of 139 properties totaling 43.8 million net rentable square", "bbox": [204.2, 581.4, 1080.5, 602.2]}, {"text": "feet. Our properties consisted of (1) 135 office properties, comprised of 102 Class A office buildings, including", "bbox": [162.5, 606.4, 1092.8, 627.2]}, {"text": "13 properties under construction, and 20 properties that support both office and technical uses, (2) three retail", "bbox": [162.5, 631.4, 1076.1, 652.2]}, {"text": "properties and (3) one hotel. In addition, we own or control 605.2 acres of land for future development. The table", "bbox": [162.5, 656.4, 1107.6, 677.2]}, {"text": "set forth below shows information relating to the properties we owned, or in which we had an ownership interest,", "bbox": [162.5, 681.4, 1108.0, 702.2]}, {"text": "at December 31, 2007. On January 7, 2008, we transferred the Mountain View properties to the Value-Added", "bbox": [162.5, 706.4, 1076.5, 727.2]}, {"text": "Fund. For the year ended December 31, 2007, the financial results of these properties are included in our", "bbox": [162.5, 731.4, 1036.4, 752.2]}, {"text": "consolidated financial results, but not included in any of our portfolio information tables or any other portfolio", "bbox": [162.5, 756.4, 1084.9, 777.2]}, {"text": "level statistics. Information relating to properties owned by the Value-Added Fund is not included in our", "bbox": [162.5, 781.4, 1035.5, 802.2]}, {"text": "portfolio information tables or any other portfolio level statistics because the Value-Added Fund invests in assets", "bbox": [162.5, 806.4, 1106.9, 827.2]}, {"text": "within our existing markets that have deficiencies in property characteristics which provide an opportunity to", "bbox": [162.5, 831.4, 1073.9, 852.2]}, {"text": "create value through repositioning, refurbishment or renovation. We therefore believe including such information", "bbox": [162.5, 856.4, 1109.6, 877.2]}, {"text": "in our portfolio tables and statistics would render the portfolio information less useful to investors. Information", "bbox": [162.5, 881.4, 1090.3, 902.2]}, {"text": "relating to the Value-Added Fund is set forth below separately.", "bbox": [162.5, 906.4, 688.5, 927.2]}, {"text": "Pr